    "201": {
      "play": "Die of this folly.   He exits, with Lords.",
      "notes": [
        "Dye of this Folly] GERVINUS (ii, 217, ed. 1872): To this curse, she who is cursed will willingly respond ‘Amen!’—HUDSON: Of course, the King means it for a curse; but he has not snap enough to make it such."
      ]
