    "21": {
      "play": "SECOND LORD, aside  As many inches as you have",
      "notes": [
        "Inches . . . Oceans] This antithesis between 'inches' and 'oceans' teases us as a possible allusion which time has hidden. But the words may signify no more than their plain meaning; inasmuch as Cloten had no 'having' in oceans, so he had no addition to his 'having in ground.'—ED. 20, 21. So would I . . . ground] Time has evaporated the wit in this sentence also,—if it ever had any.—ED."
      ]
