    "37": {
      "play": "The shes of Italy should not betray",
      "notes": [
        "The Shees] See ‘’Twixt two such She’s.’—I, vii, 47. For other instances where ‘he’ and ‘she’ are used for man and woman, see ABBOTT, § 224."
