        "Confections] DOWDEN: That is, compounded drugs, as in V, v, 289. 21, 22. is’t not meete That I did] ABBOTT (§ 370): Here, as in ‘It is time he came,’ the action is regarded as one ‘meet’ in time past, as well as in the future."
      ]
