    "23": {
      "play": "Other conclusions? I will try the forces",
      "notes": []
    },
    "24": {
      "play": "Of these thy compounds on such creatures as",
      "notes": []
    },
    "25": {
      "play": "We count not worth the hanging—but none human—",
      "notes": []
