    },
    "36": {
      "play": "CLOTEN: A stranger, and I not know on ’t?",
      "notes": []
    },
    "37": {
      "play": "SECOND LORD, aside  He’s a strange fellow himself and",
      "notes": []
    },
    "38": {
      "play": "knows it not.",
      "notes": []
    },
    "39": {
      "play": "FIRST LORD: There’s an Italian come, and ’tis thought",
      "notes": []
    },
    "40": {
      "play": "one of Leonatus’ friends.",
      "notes": []
    },
    "41": {
      "play": "CLOTEN: Leonatus? A banished rascal; and he’s another,",
      "notes": []
    },
    "42": {
      "play": "whatsoever he be. Who told you of this stranger?",
      "notes": []
    },
    "43": {
      "play": "FIRST LORD: One of your Lordship’s pages.",
      "notes": []
    },
    "44": {
      "play": "CLOTEN: Is it fit I went to look upon him? Is there no",
