      "notes": [
        "out-sell] SCHMIDT (Lex.): That is, exceeded it in value. See where Cloten speaks of Imogen and of her superiority above other women, ‘and she of all compounded Out-sells them all.’—III, v, 93."
      ]
    },
    "135": {
      "play": "And yet enriched it too. She gave it me",
