        "I greeue my selfe, etc.] Compare Hermione's pathetic speech to Leontes, in The Wint. Tale: ‘how this will grieue you, When you shall come to clearer knowledge that You thus haue publish’d me.’—II, i, 119 (of this ed.).—Ed."
      ]
