      "notes": [
        "(You rather) mine being yours] I am not sure that this parenthesis should be discarded, or at least its place supplied by commas, as by Rowe. Does it not give emphasis to the idea that the gods, far sooner than ordinary men, should be willing to take a light piece, since they coined it?—ED."
      ]
