    "146": {
      "play": "CYMBELINE: Wherefore ey’st him so?",
      "notes": [
        "Wherefore ey’st him so] LADY MARTIN (p. 216): How intently Imogen has been absorbed in watching Iachimo is further shown by the circumstance that, though near her late companions of the cave, she has not observed them."
      ]
    },
    "147": {
      "play": "IMOGEN, as Fidele",
      "notes": []
