      "play": "The thankings of a king.",
      "notes": []
    },
    "526": {
      "play": "POSTHUMUS: I am, sir,",
      "notes": [
        "I am Sir] The Text. Notes reveal the struggles of editors to supply a gap in the metre, which the pause between two speeches renders needless.—Ed."
      ]
